<code>sup()</code></a> para formatar uma string:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> superText <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'superscript'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> subText <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'subscript'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'This is what a '</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> superText<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">sup</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">' looks like.'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// This is what a &lt;sup&gt;superscript&lt;/sup&gt; looks like</span>\n\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'This is what a '</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> subText<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">sub</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">' looks like.'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// This is what a &lt;sub&gt;subscript&lt;/sub&gt; looks like.</span>\n</code></pre></div>","titleAsText":"Usando os métodos sub() e sup()"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificação","title":"Especificação","isH3